snippet.title: [OFFICAL] SS!UNDERSWAP YouTube Announcement!
snippet.description:
That's right! 

Here's home! - https://discord.gg/ADzrD8a

But on a serious note. 
Here is our first official video on SS! UNDERSWAP
SS!UNDERSWAP is a fan-game on Undertale involving the word "Swap"
If it seems interesting check out our Gamejolt and give it a follow!

https://gamejolt.com/games/SSUnderswap/456789

If you want to as well, give us a like and sub. Maybe even share this video to let people know about SS!UNDERSWAP!

Stay Sensational


Thanks to Snowy for making this video.
Check him out. Their pretty spicy.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTLNXyWEorMo2h-jZfOj_Vw/videos?view_as=subscriber
